article_id:1893,category_name:News,title_name:A New Summon Showcase, Cursed Connections (Part Two), Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A summon showcase, Cursed Connections (Part Two), went live at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609999200"></span>! This summon showcase includes a limited-time adventurer and dragon. Featured adventurers and dragons also have a boosted appearance rate!</div><div><br></div><div>Newly added limited-time featured adventurer:</div><div>■Adventurer</div><div>5★ Yoshitsune (water/close-range manacaster)</div><div><br></div><div>Note: The standard attacks of the close-range manacaster arc outwards, making it ideal for close-range crowd control. By attacking foes at point-blank range, you can do even more damage.</div><div><br></div><div>Returning limited-time featured dragon:</div><div>■Dragon</div><div>5★ Gozu Tenno (flame)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>In this summon showcase, the following limited-time adventurers and dragons make their return. These adventurers and dragons are not featured in this showcase.</strong></span></div><div><br></div><div>Returning limited-time adventurers and dragons:</div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Seimei (flame/wand)</div><div>5★ Mitsuhide (light/dagger)</div><div>5★ Nobunaga (flame/blade)</div><div>5★ Ieyasu (shadow/blade)</div><div>4★ Chitose (light/wand)</div><div>4★ Sazanka (shadow/axe)</div><div>4★ Addis (wind/blade)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragons</div><div>5★ Daikokuten (light)</div><div>5★ Marishiten (shadow)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>Wyrmsigils may only be redeemed from the same summon showcase that they were earned from. Wyrmsigils earned from the Cursed Connections (Part One) showcase cannot be redeemed from the Cursed Connections (Part Two) showcase. The 5★ adventurer Seimei is not be eligible to redeem for wyrmsigils from the Cursed Connections (Part Two) showcase.</strong></span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for showcase summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609999200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1610603999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurer and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
